rows.label: qst100201_msg0001
rows.name:
Oi! We won the auction for
this merchandise first!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0002
rows.name:
What are you mistaken about? We
were the first to win the bid.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0003
rows.name: Hyaaa...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0004
rows.name:
Now, Hiyaya-san, I will pay the
designated amount! Please take the
cargo to the Superbian ship immediately!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0005
rows.name:
Hold it! You Superbian thief! Trying
to loot us like you did Gula?

rows.label: qst100201_msg0006
rows.name: Momomo...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0007
rows.name:
I will not stand for such
slander... Gula was acquired
through proper procedures...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0008
rows.name:
But no matter how I explain
it, a barbaric Invidian would
never be able to understand!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0009
rows.name:
What did you say?! Then,
as you wish, by force...!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0010
rows.name: Momomomo! No violence, mo!!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0011
rows.name:
This is Avaritia! Don't bring
your outside disputes here, mo!!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0012
rows.name:
Then what are we supposed
to do?! Hiyaya-san...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0013
rows.name:
In the first place, this auction...
There was a problem with the Avaritia
Trade Guild's proceedings...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0014
rows.name: Hyaaa... Th-that's...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0015
rows.name:
Oh! Driver-san! Heeelp!
Please help me, mo! No
violence! Hiyaya is scared, mo!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0016
rows.name:
These two groups won the bid
for the star item, the Delta
Box, for the same amount, mo.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0017
rows.name:
But there's only one in stock...
and they've started to argue, mo!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0018
rows.name:
Wait a minute... There's only
one in stock, so why were two
winning bids confirmed?

rows.label: qst100201_msg0019
rows.name:
Um... That's because Hiyaya
was looking away...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0020
rows.name:
We're being dragged into your
mistake, Hiyaya-san! What are
you going to do about it?!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0021
rows.name:
Mohyaaa... If only there
was another Delta Box...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0022
rows.name:
Momo?! Will you bring me
another Delta Box, mo?

rows.label: qst100201_msg0023
rows.name:
For Hiyaya's sake...
Thank you, mo... *sob*

rows.label: qst100201_msg0024
rows.name:
You should be able to find a
Delta Box by salvaging in the
deep parts of the Cloud Sea, mo.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0025
rows.name:
You have to dive deep, so...
I'll give you Hiyaya's secret
Quest Cylinder (Temp), mo.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0026
rows.name:
Please come back quickly before
Hiyaya's liver gets scared, mo!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0101
rows.name:
Please find one Delta Box
super-duper fast, mo!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0102
rows.name: Hiyaya's fate is in your hands, mo...
